[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    439[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206m|[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mEncryption[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;192;197;206m|[38;2;192;197;206m Connect call recordings: SSE-KMS with customer-managed keys, S3 bucket lifecycle to colder storage tiers, retention per institutional and state-specific medical-records-retention requirements. DynamoDB tables: customer-managed KMS at rest. Secrets Manager: customer-managed KMS. Lambda environment variables encrypted at rest with KMS. Lambda log groups: KMS-encrypted. TLS in transit for all back-office API calls. [38;2;192;197;206m|[K
